DatetimeBornNative
/ A datetime cast lands the value as datetime.@this (born-native), backed by DateTimeOffset —
/ not a Data-wrapping-a-Data. Type is "datetime" and its parts read off the wrapper.
- set %dt% = "2026-01-01T12:00:00Z" as datetime
- assert %dt.Type.Name% equals "datetime"
- assert %dt.Year% equals 2026
